        <h2>Who should choose Buildertrend</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Custom homebuilders managing complex owner selections across multiple projects</li>
          <li>Contractors with established teams where the larger ecosystem matters</li>
          <li>Builders who want the most polished client-facing experience</li>
